summaries.short: While Sr. Avila and Ivan take on a complex case, Maria and Octavio hide somewhere they hope is beyond Avila's reach.
summaries.full: While Sr. Avila and Ivan take on a complex case, Maria and Octavio hide somewhere they hope is beyond Avila's reach as she has the evidence to nail her husband. Avila has suspicions about the circumstances surrounding the death of his son Emiliano and decides to get to the bottom of things.

summaries.short: After Avila ignores the Board's decision, which leaves a colleague dead, the Board must reconvene.
summaries.full: After Avila ignores the Board's decision, which leaves a colleague dead, the Board must reconvene. Avila also gets a new assignment involving Sr. Juarez - a Board member - whose son feels he is ready to take his father's place, and wants speed up the natural course of events.
